{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "0a1b2c3d4e5f6789",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -760,
      "y": -520,
      "width": 1580,
      "height": 1040,
      "label": "Kubernetes 网络全景：从身份、入口、策略到排障",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1a2b3c4d5e6f7081",
      "type": "file",
      "x": -160,
      "y": -470,
      "width": 430,
      "height": 240,
      "file": "Spaces/2-Area/云服务和部署/Kubernetes 网络全景 - 从 Pod 到 Service、Ingress、Gateway 与 NetworkPolicy.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "2a3b4c5d6e7f8091",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -700,
      "y": -440,
      "width": 390,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## 1. Pod 网络模型\n\n- 最小网络单元是 Pod\n- 同 Pod 容器共享 IP、端口空间、localhost\n- 每个 Pod 拿到集群内唯一 IP\n- 普通应用不应该依赖 Pod IP 的长期稳定性"
    },
    {
      "id": "3a4b5c6d7e8f9012",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -700,
      "y": -170,
      "width": 390,
      "height": 250,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## 2. Pod 级端口\n\n`containerPort`：声明容器端口，不是防火墙。\n\n`hostPort`：把容器端口绑定到所在节点端口，适合 DaemonSet / node agent。\n\n`hostNetwork`：Pod 直接使用宿主网络，隔离最弱。"
    },
    {
      "id": "4a5b6c7d8e9f0123",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -700,
      "y": 170,
      "width": 390,
      "height": 230,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "## 3. CNI 数据面\n\nCNI 负责 IPAM、veth/路由/Overlay/ENI/eBPF、NetworkPolicy 执行。\n\n先确认：Pod CIDR、Service CIDR、MTU、是否支持策略、是否替代 kube-proxy。"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a6b7c8d9e0f1234",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -170,
      "y": -150,
      "width": 430,
      "height": 240,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## 4. Service 抽象\n\nService = 稳定入口 + 动态后端。\n\n核心链路：\n\nDNS -> ClusterIP / Service VIP -> kube-proxy 或 eBPF -> EndpointSlice -> PodIP:targetPort"
    },
    {
      "id": "6a7b8c9d0e1f2345",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 360,
      "y": -440,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 250,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## 5. 入口类型\n\n- ClusterIP：集群内部\n- NodePort：每节点固定端口\n- LoadBalancer：云 / 裸金属 LB\n- Ingress：HTTP/HTTPS host/path\n- Gateway API：新一代多协议路由"
    },
    {
      "id": "7a8b9c0d1e2f3456",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 360,
      "y": -110,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 230,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## 6. 策略与安全\n\nNetworkPolicy 是 allow-list API。\n\n默认通常全通；Pod 被策略选中后，对应方向进入隔离。\n\n是否生效取决于 CNI。"
    },
    {
      "id": "8a9b0c1d2e3f4567",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 230,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## 7. 排障入口\n\n按层定位：\n\nPod -> CNI -> DNS -> Service / EndpointSlice -> kube-proxy/eBPF -> LB / Ingress / Gateway -> NetworkPolicy / Mesh"
    },
    {
      "id": "9a0b1c2d3e4f5678",
      "type": "file",
      "x": -160,
      "y": 170,
