    },
    {
      "id": "5b6c7d8e9f0a1234",
      "type": "file",
      "x": 820,
      "y": 90,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 190,
      "file": "Spaces/1-Project/2025年ack和k8s学习回顾/kubernetes复习计划/DNS 与服务发现.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "6b7c8d9e0f1a2345",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 820,
      "y": 350,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 210,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## hostPort 记忆钩子\n\nhostPort 是“这个节点上这个端口”的语义。\n\nService 是“这组 Pod 作为一个服务”的语义。\n\n业务入口默认先考虑 Service / Ingress / Gateway。"
    }
  ],
